The Setup for Windows version currently using InnoSetup (http://www.jrsoftware.org/isinfo.php)

To compile the setup script qsvn.wxs you must first copy any necessary libraries and binaries:

intl3_svn.dll
libapr.dll
libapriconv.dll
libaprutil.dll
libdb43.dll
libeay32.dll
ssleay32.dll

Microsoft_VC80_CRT_x86.msm
policy_8_0_Microsoft_VC80_CRT_x86.msm

QtCore4.dll
QtGui4.dll


Then you will install the WiX toolkit found at http://wix.sf.net.

Compile the msi with:

candle qsvn.wxs
light -out qsvn.msi qsvn.wixobj \path\to\wix\ui\wixui_mondo.xlib
